<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Employee Manager</h1>
            <p>Integrated Attendance & Leave Management System</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Proposal for Integrated Attendance & Leave Management System</h2>
                <p>Dear Eric,</p>
                <p>Thank you for your interest in our comprehensive <strong>Employee Manager</strong> solution. This system is designed to streamline your employee attendance and leave management processes, bringing transparency, efficiency, and control to your operations.</p>
                <p>Below, please find a detailed overview of how the system works for both Administrators (using the Web Dashboard) and Employees (using the Mobile App).</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">System Overview</h2>
                <p>The <strong>Employee Manager</strong> is a two-part system:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Web Admin Dashboard:</strong> For company management, policy setting, and oversight.</li>
                    <li><strong>Employee Mobile App:</strong> For daily check-ins, check-outs, and leave requests.</li>
                </ol>
                <p>The system uses <strong>geolocation technology</strong> to ensure attendance is only recorded when an employee is physically at their designated workplace, eliminating buddy-punching and ensuring accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Part 1: Web Admin Dashboard</h2>
                <p>The Admin Dashboard is your command center. You will use it to set up the company, define rules, and manage your Employees.</p>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">1. Admin Login & Security</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> You and your managers log in through a secure web portal using unique credentials.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Ensures that only authorized personnel can access sensitive company and employee data.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/login.JPG" alt="Admin Login" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">2. Company Profile & Branch Creation</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> After the first login, you will create your company profile. You can then add multiple branches or offices (e.g., "Head Office," "Downtown Branch").</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To structure your organization within the system for precise management.</p>
                    <div class="two-column">
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container">
                                <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/compnay.JPG" alt="Company Profile" class="fixed-image-small">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container">
                                 <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/compan2.JPG" alt="Branch Management" class="fixed-image-small">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">3. Geolocation Setup for Offices</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> For each branch, you will define its physical location by setting a <strong>Geofence</strong>. You pinpoint the office location on a map and set a radius (e.g., 100 meters) within which employees can check in.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> This is the foundation for location-based attendance. It ensures employees are at the office when they clock in or out.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/image%20scann.JPG" alt="Geolocation Setup" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">4. Configure Working Days & Shifts</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> You define the official working days for the company (e.g., Monday to Friday) and can create specific shifts (e.g., "Morning Shift: 9 AM - 5 PM").</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Establishes the standard operating schedule, which the system uses to calculate late arrivals, early departures, and overtime.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/working-hours-setting.JPG" alt="Working Days Settings" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">5. Leave Policy Management</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> You can fully customize the types of leave available to employees (e.g., Annual Leave, Sick Leave, Maternity Leave). For each type, you set the entitlement (e.g., 21 days per year), accrual rate, and carry-over rules.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Automates leave allocation and ensures all employee requests adhere to company policy.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/leave%20settings.JPG" alt="Leave Settings" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">6. Employee Registration & Assignment</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> You can register new employees into the system, input their details, and assign them to a specific company branch and department.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Creates unique employee profiles that are linked to their specific workplace's geofence and leave policies.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/add-employee.JPG" alt="Add Employee" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">7. Leave Request Approval/Rejection</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> All leave requests submitted by employees through their mobile app appear in a central dashboard. You can review the request, see the employee's leave balance, and <strong>Approve</strong> or <strong>Reject</strong> it with a single click. Notifications are sent automatically.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Streamlines the approval process and maintains a digital record of all leave.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/leave-list%20approval.JPG" alt="Leave Approval" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">8. Reports & Analytics</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> Generate real-time reports on attendance summaries, leave balances, late arrivals, and absence trends for individuals, teams, or the entire company.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Provides valuable insights for payroll processing and managerial decision-making.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/attendance-list.JPG" alt="Attendance Reports" class="fixed-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Part 2: Employee Mobile App</h2>
                <p>The Employee App is simple, intuitive, and designed for daily use on the go.</p>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">1. Employee Login</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> Employees log in using credentials provided by the admin.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Securely accesses their personal dashboard.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/Screenshot_2025-10-16-16-29-57-74_12e79c5781c294dddb0c7c951d63e8be.jpg" alt="Employee Login" class="mobile-image-small">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">2. Attendance (Check-In / Check-Out)</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> The main screen of the app features prominent <strong>Check-In</strong> and <strong>Check-Out</strong> buttons. The app uses GPS to verify the employee is within the office's pre-set geofence. Attendance is only allowed if the location is correct.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Provides a foolproof method for recording work hours.</p>
                    <div class="two-column">
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container">
                                <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/Screenshot_2025-10-16-16-29-57-74_12e79c5781c294dddb0c7c951d63e8be.jpg" alt="Check-In Screen" class="mobile-image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container"> 
                                <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/Screenshot_2025-10-16-16-31-24-52_12e79c5781c294dddb0c7c951d63e8be.jpg" alt="Check-Out Screen" class="mobile-image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">3. Leave Request Submission</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> Employees can tap a "Request Leave" button, select the type of leave, choose start and end dates, and add a reason. The app automatically shows their remaining balance for that leave type.</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Empowers employees to manage their time off easily and in compliance with company rules.</p>
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/Screenshot_2025-10-16-16-36-00-82_12e79c5781c294dddb0c7c951d63e8be.jpg" alt="Leave Request" class="mobile-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">4. View Attendance History & Leave Status</h3>
                    <p><strong>Process:</strong> Employees can view their own check-in/check-out history and the current status of their submitted leave requests (e.g., Pending, Approved, Rejected).</p>
                    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Promotes transparency and allows employees to track their own records.</p>
                    <div class="two-column">
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container">
                                <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/Screenshot_2025-10-16-16-37-55-42_12e79c5781c294dddb0c7c951d63e8be.jpg" alt="Attendance History" class="mobile-image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="column">
                            <div class="image-container">
                                <img src="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/WhatsApp%20Image%202025-10-16%20at%2018.43.09_38780638.jpg" alt="Leave Status" class="mobile-image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Why Partner With Us?</h2>
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong>Increased Accountability</strong>
                        <p>Geolocation ensures accurate attendance recording.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong>Reduced Administrative Burden</strong>
                        <p>Automates leave management and record-keeping.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong>Data-Driven Decisions</strong>
                        <p>Access to real-time reports and analytics.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong>Improved Transparency</strong>
                        <p>A clear and fair system for both management and employees.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <strong>Scalability</strong>
                        <p>The system grows with your business, easily accommodating new branches and employees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Ready to Transform Your Employees Management?</h2>
                <p>We are confident that the <strong>Employee Manager</strong> system will bring significant value to your company. We would be delighted to schedule a live demo at your convenience to walk you through every feature.</p>
                <p>Please let us know a time that works for you.</p>
                <a href="https://worker-attendance-puce.vercel.app/" class="cta-button">Schedule a Demo</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p><strong>Pascal NDACYAYISENGA</strong><br>
                Software Developer<br>
                0781495385</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
